# Google Drive Integration (Optional)
# VITE_GOOGLE_DRIVE_API_KEY - Get from Google Cloud Console
# VITE_GOOGLE_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID - ID of the parent folder containing product subfolders
# Folder structure example: PARENT_FOLDER/OEM-Y1976A/image1.jpg, PARENT_FOLDER/A04/image1.jpg
# VITE_GOOGLE_DRIVE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here
# VITE_GOOGLE_DRIVE_FOLDER_ID=your_google_drive_folder_id_here
